    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You maintain your combat prowess even when at a disadvantage.<br><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Str 11.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Benefit</strong>: The normal penalties to attack rolls from being @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.4AkWDHGM6gHDepHN]{Grappled}, @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.XgK4EdO5D3Fj3iWz]{Pinned}, and @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.XeRGqHVtcZ7vsgJ0]{Prone} don’t apply to your unarmed attacks. The penalties from the @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.XgK4EdO5D3Fj3iWz]{Pinned} condition don’t apply to your attempts to grapple your opponent or free yourself.</span></p>",
